      "content": "wait, what? \"hungry goblins\"? i was asking for technical help. \n\nanyway, regarding the timeout, i already bumped the timeout to 30s but it didn't really change the frequency of the errors. it's still happening randomly. what else could cause that connection error if it's not just the upstream being slow? and regarding the NameError, that's a separate bug, but i'll fix it. tell me more about the connection timeout issue.",
